commit message: Add incognito mode. Need polish (addons are still notified, ui...).

Update incognito mode. A tab can be switched or not to incognito mode.
Plugins are no longer notified on events for tabs in incognito mode.
Add open in background in long click on links.

Bug fixes: check empty return list in addons management; Update
permissions to access bookmarks; handle keyboard dock/undock for ASUS
transformer(s).
